Executive Profile
B. Christopher DiSantis  Chief Executive Officer, President and Director, Verso CorporationAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships45--
Background

		Mr. B. Christopher Disantis, also known as Chris, serves as Vice-President of Ag Industries, Inc. Mr. Disantis the Chief Executive Officer and President of Verso Corporation since February 01, 2017. Mr. Disantis served as a Consultant at Carpenter Technology Corp. He served as the Chief Executive Officer and President at Carpenter Technology Corporation. Mr. Disantis served as the Chief Executive Officer and President of Latrobe Specialty Metals, Inc. (formerly Latrobe ... Specialty Steel Company) since January 2011. He served as the President and Chief Operating Officer at Hawk Corp. from March 2008 to December 2, 2011. He served as the President of Friction Products & Performance Racing Segments at Hawk Corp until December 02, 2010. He served as the President of Wellman Products Group at Hawk Corp. since May 2006. He served as the President of Hawk Motors Inc., since May 2003. He served as the President of Hawk Precision Components Group Inc., from January 2004 to May 2006. He served as the President of Friction Products and Performance Racing group at Hawk Corp., since May 2006. He served as Vice President of Manufacturing Innovation at Hawk Corp., since March 2006. He also served as Acting Vice President of Manufacturing Innovation at Hawk Corp., since March 27, 2006. Mr. Disantis has a wealth of financial and operating experience. He served as Vice President of Seabury Metals in New York City, where he was directly responsible for the acquisition program and start-up of an aluminum dross recycler. He has been Independent Director of Hardinge Inc. since July 07, 2016. He has been a Director of Verso Corporation February 1, 2017. He has been a Director of Latrobe Specialty Metals, Inc. since May 2011. Mr. DiSantis has degrees in Math and Economics from Dartmouth College.Read Full Background




