B. Christopher DiSantis

Age : 45Public asset : 723,547 USDLinked companies :  Verso Corp -  Hardinge Inc. 





Summary 



Mr. B. C. DiSantis is President at H-D Advanced Manufacturing Co.He is on the Board of Directors at Verso Corp., Hardinge, Inc. and Channel Products, Inc. Mr. DiSantis was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Latrobe Specialty Steel Co., President, Chief Executive Officer & Director by Latrobe Specialty Metals, Inc., President by Wellman Products Group, Inc., President by Hawk Motors, Inc., President by NetShape Technologies, Inc., President & Chief Operating Officer by Hawk Corp., President by Hawk Precision Components Group, Inc., and President by Hawk Racing, Inc.He also served on the board at JFC Holding Corp. He received his undergraduate degree from Dartmouth College.



